['5', 'I have been looking for the perfect hair tool to lift my fine hair the day after I have washed it. This fits the bill better than anything else I have tried. It works quickly and effectively. I have the thinner 19 mm InStyler which works really well on my short hair. Also the body stays in all day. I would certainly recommend this product but if you have kids be careful they are not around when you use it as the barrel is so hot it could easily cause a burn if touched.', [2, 2, 2, 2, 9], [2, 3, 2, 22, 52]]